{"tid":838672,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GOT7代言Adidas Originals成品牌全球大使","createTime":"2018-09-27T10:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T10:42:05.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8d156d7603014bcafa058f953288ffd26ab24ac9","tid":838672,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"9月24日GOT7官方頻道釋出了主打歌Lullaby另一支獨特主題影片，影片裡GOT7七人帥氣穿著Adidas Original黑白運動服表演著他們新主打歌Lullaby，愛迪達官方在這個月稍早宣布GOT7成為他們Adidas Origianls的品牌全球大使。<br />\n<br />\n與全球知名運動服品牌愛迪達的合作更進一步證明了GOT7全球人氣和吸引力,且在成功地完成了他們Eyes On You世界巡迴演唱會後也帶來了更多人氣。除了愛迪達以外，GOT7也獲得了其他品牌的代言包括保養品品牌 ；此外，GOT7成員們也榮獲南韓消防局的名譽大使。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h-DsGlNR5vk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dh-DsGlNR5vk&d=MMfzIUeDDF2SfcWtqNfQN0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=d0c283ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h-DsGlNR5vk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1ArL6tC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1ArL6tC.jpg&h=b756338f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/X66NSV2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FX66NSV2.jpg&h=c260f86b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.allkpop.com/upload/2018/09/af_org/24064936/got7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.allkpop.com%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2Faf_org%2F24064936%2Fgot7.jpg&h=860bfdb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好想同JACKSON著同一套<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aeef5249cc7758d62063333e03fe1abcdf9e1a5","tid":838672,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T10:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"h